Pendulum Effect
 You cannot Pendulum Summon monsters, except "Nekroz" or "Sephira" monsters. This effect cannot be negated.

 Monster Effect
 You can Tribute this card from your hand or face-up from your side of the field; Tribute monsters from your hand or field, then Ritual Summon 1 "Nekroz" Ritual Monster from your hand whose Level exactly equals the total Levels of those monsters. You can only use this effect of "Sword Saint of the Nekroz - Sephira Saber" once per turn.
